title: Third Annual La Cita Event Slated for Boca Raton Resort
text:
Last updated: 04:30 PM ET, Thu August 20 2015 Third Annual La Cita Event Slated for Boca Raton Resort Travel Agent | Claudette Covey | August 20,   Thinkstock 
Early next month, buyers and sellers specializing in Latin America will converge at Floridaâ€™s Boca Raton Resort & Club for La Cita de las Americas, a one-on-one trade show event designed to boost inbound travel to the U.S. from Mexico, Central and South America and the Caribbean.
